getValue

Class UserValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • getValue.UserValue

  • public class UserValue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to obtain statistics about a user. Given the user's name and the location of the server database, a string with the specific statistic will be returned.
    Author:
    Nicholas Ingalls

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructor and Description
      UserValue(java.lang.String data, java.lang.String username)
      Constructs a new object with a string containing the database location and a string containing the username.
